
test_teec: Demonstrate trusted communication between
           HLOS Application(teectest) and CMRT container

teectest is a sample application built using TEE Client API
which is higher-level API for HLOS Applications.

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run test_teec.img

To start communication between Trusted Application and HLOS Application:
$ teectest

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
